      'th': '<p>????????????????????? <code>grid-column</code> ??? <code>grid-row</code> ?????????????????????, ???????????????????????????? <code>grid-area</code> ????????????????????????????????? slash: <code>grid-row-start</code>, <code>grid-column-start</code>, <code>grid-row-end</code>, ??????? <code>grid-column-end</code>.</p><p>?????????????????????????????????? <code>grid-area: 1 / 1 / 3 / 6;</code>.</p>',
