      'en': '<p>Now the water and poison are alternating, even though all of the weeds are at the start of your garden. Set the <code>order</code> of the poisons to remedy this.</p>',
      'hi': '<p>?? ???? ?? ??? ????-???? ?? ?? ??? ???, ??? ?? ??? ??????? ???? ????? ?? ?????? ??? ???? ??? <code>order</code> ??? ??? ???? ?? ??? ??? ???</p>',
      'lv': '<p>Tagad udens un inde parklajas, neskatoties uz to, ka visas nezales ir tava darza sakuma. Lai to labotu, nomaini indes elementu <code>order</code> vertibu.</p>',
      'ro': '<p>Acum apa ?i otrava alterneaza, chiar daca toate buruienile sunt la începutul gradinii tale. Schimba valoarea proprieta?ii <code>order</code> a otravei pentru a repara acest lucru.</p>',
      'zh-cn': '<p>???????????????,???????????????????????????<code>order</code>???????!</p>',
      'zh-tw': '<p>???????????????,??????????????????????????? <code>order</code> ???????!</p>',
      'tr': '<p>Artik yabani otlarin hepsi bahçenizin basinda olsa da, su ve zehir karisik yerlesmis durumda. Bunu düzeltmek için zehirlerin <code>order</code> degerlerini ayarlayin.</p>',
